      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"it's just so heavy. when you say it's okay to stop trying... it feels like there's no real way to actually stop. like, how do you even deal with the fact that everything you do—every breath, every day, every little plan—is just a waste of time because the end is inevitable? it feels like a trap. like why stay in the room when the house is literally on fire?\"",
